room_title: Escape room "Masquerade Manor" by Escape Room 831 in Salinas
room_description:
Wealthy and famous composer Ludovico Manin is the prime suspect in a recent, high-profile crime.
Tonight, during his annual Masquerade Ball, is your best chance to look for evidence against him. Disguised as guests, you must infiltrate the ball, find proof of Maninâ€™s guilt, and leave without being detected. Can you find the stolen object and escape in time?
